I started to do choreo a few years back when I was in a show and going through a rough time in my life. I have recently decided to bring back to life some of those pieces in different light. Although this is a vulnerable side for me to embrace, I hope you all can enjoy a bit of musical theater history that I try to embody in my choreo. Thank you to all my amazing dancers in this for allowing me to create something I didn’t think would ever see the light again. Trust me there is more to come, enjoy!
